This is sorta on subject, but off subject at the same time.  I have found recently that when I run up on a corpse and send a tell to that person, if they happen to be online, asking if they'd like me to drag their corpse anywhere, that I haven't been getting many replies.  Even in bad agro zones such as Fungus Grove.  While it wouldn't take me much to drag someone's corpse to wherever they'd like in zone, any sort of reply telling me they don't need the assistance would be nice.<br>
<br>
Back on subject, I find it amusing how some people say they are casting C3 or HoS or Virtue for donations (get that DONATIONS) and when you offer up a few plat, they look agast at you and mouth off at ya for thinking of donating such a lowly amount.<br>
